  <section id="tone-spectrum" data-slide-index="2" data-lesson-slug="tone-spectrum" class="module-section py-16">
    <h2>Tone Spectrum & Practice</h2>

    <p class="text-lg text-n600 mb-6">
      Playbook has one voice but four tone registers. Same person, different conversations. This lesson teaches you when to use each one.
    </p>

    <h3 id="the-four-registers">The four registers</h3>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 my-6">
      <!-- Playful / Witty -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-teal bg-white shadow-sm p-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-1.5">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-navy">Playful / Witty</p>
          <span class="text-sm text-n400 ml-auto">Tier 1</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-n700 mb-1">Myth-busting, quizzes, social cards, hook content</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-n500 italic">"Share this with the friend who thinks they have a 'system.'"</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Confident / Informative -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-navy bg-white shadow-sm p-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-1.5">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-navy/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-navy">Confident / Informative</p>
          <span class="text-sm text-n400 ml-auto">Tier 1</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-n700 mb-1">Odds education, tool explanations, how-it-works, game guides</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-n500 italic">"The house edge on blackjack is 0.5%. On slots, it's 2–15%. Now you know."</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Warm / Direct -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-orange bg-white shadow-sm p-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-1.5">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-navy">Warm / Direct</p>
          <span class="text-sm text-n400 ml-auto">Tier 2</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-n700 mb-1">Check-ins, support access, limit notifications, at-risk touchpoints</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-n500 italic">"Need to talk? Free, confidential, 24/7."</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Celebratory -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-success bg-white shadow-sm p-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-1.5">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-navy">Celebratory</p>
          <span class="text-sm text-n400 ml-auto">Tier 1</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-n700 mb-1">Quiz results, limit set confirmation, achievement moments</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-n500 italic">"You scored 8/10. Sharper than most. Challenge a friend?"</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 id="matching-registers-to-context">Matching registers to context</h3>

    <p>
      The register isn't random. It follows the context. Here's a quick decision guide:
    </p>

    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Context</th><th>Register</th><th>Why</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Myth-busting article / social post</td><td>Playful / Witty</td><td>Competing for attention — earn it with insight</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Odds explainer / onboarding / tool description</td><td>Confident / Informative</td><td>Math, mechanics, and setup — clarity matters</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Session reminder</td><td>Warm / Direct</td><td>Practical check-in, gentle nudge</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Self-exclusion page</td><td>Warm / Direct (serious)</td><td>Zero humor, maximum clarity</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Quiz results / achievement moments</td><td>Celebratory</td><td>"Here's what you know" energy</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <KeyConcept title="One rule for Warm / Direct" icon="bolt">
      <p>
        When the register is Warm / Direct, humor drops to zero. This is Tier 2 territory — support
        access, crisis moments, take-a-break flows. The voice stays the same (generous, honest,
        non-judgmental) but the tone is plain, clear, and immediate. No jokes. No cleverness. Just
        the information the player needs.
      </p>
    </KeyConcept>
  </section>

