          <text x="510" y="81" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#1B2838" font-weight="700">Respectful of</text>
          <text x="510" y="97" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#1B2838" font-weight="700">intelligence</text>
