    <h3 id="the-humor-register">The humor register</h3>

    <p>
      Humor is core to Playbook — it separates the brand from compliance content. But the
      <strong>register</strong> of humor varies:
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-orange/30 bg-orange/5 p-5 shadow-sm">
